{"tid":2417828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港監察呼籲抵英BNO盡早登記做選民","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T06:06:55.000Z","uid":305299,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"129eab205c84f465ddcb45b63a2d952c1989928d","tid":2417828,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1363590097329938432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1363590097329938432&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=19584c46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1363590097329938432&h=9e691b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1363590097329938432</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = <br />\n今年5月英國就會舉行地方選舉，而且好多地區都會選出當地嘅警務處處長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(冇錯，選警務處處長，香港冇得選，但英國可以，正唔正?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 所以請到咗英國嘅BNO把握自己嘅權利，登記做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下係選民登記要求：<br />\n<br />\n- 以合法身份通常居住英國 (有人未夠半年都成功登記)<br />\n- 英聯邦公民 (BNO就係其中一種)<br />\n- 夠18歲 (蘇格蘭同威爾士地方選舉可以16歲)<br />\n最下面有選民登記傳送門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">注意</span></span>：<span class=\"red\">請善用身份剔除及匿名登記</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗選舉嘅公正，以及畀政商界參考，英國政府係有兩本選民名冊：公開選民名冊 (open register) 同一般選民名冊 (electoral register) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，公開名冊係啊豬啊狗都可以睇到，只要你肯畀錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公開名冊係會列出你個名同地址，所以政客、商人、學者、記者等等都會時不時畀錢買來睇同研究，而依家依個時勢，唔排除會有英國以外嘅勢力都會想買來睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以建議，可以考慮選擇將自己嘅資料從公開名冊入面剔除 (opt out)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺網上登記或者聯絡各地嘅選民登記辦事處就可以剔除身份，下面有傳送門，而且剔除公開名冊入面嘅身份係唔會影響投票權，所以可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而一般選民名冊就應該有齊每位選民嘅資料，但一般名冊就只有特定理由先可以睇到，例如：核對貸款申請、競選活動等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果都仲係有擔心，就可以透過匿名方式登記做選民 (registering anonymously)，咁樣就會兩本名冊都搵唔到你嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但匿名登記就唔係人人都可以申請，而且申請程序比較複雜，一般係畀暴力受害者本人、佢嘅同屋人士申請，目的係費事被發現之後再次畀人尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過今時今日嘅局勢，可能有部份BNO都有咁嘅需要，細仔申請匿名登記嘅資格同手續請睇下面傳送門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 網上選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=96ca5d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 郵寄選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fregister-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=11ab560c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 剔除公開名冊資料 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/electoral-register/opt-out-of-the-open-register\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Felectoral-register%2Fopt-out-of-the-open-register&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=8f090e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/electoral-register/opt-out-of-the-open-register</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 匿名選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-anonymously\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fregister-to-vote-anonymously&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=906c3ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-anonymously</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 內政大臣彭黛玲聲明 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement/hong-kong-british-national-overseas-visa-policy-statement-plain-text-version\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fhong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement%2Fhong-kong-british-national-overseas-visa-policy-statement-plain-text-version&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=92127512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/hong-kong-bno-visa-policy-statement/hong-kong-british-national-overseas-visa-policy-statement-plain-text-version</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 單純些牙 = = = = =<br />\n國安法下, 點答英國人口普查「種族」及「國族認同」好?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390229</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 開心些牙 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/ima_hksiuwaga肉豬/show/5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fima_hksiuwaga%E8%82%89%E8%B1%AC%2Fshow%2F5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=05b4c19c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/ima_hksiuwaga肉豬/show/5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WmdjQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WmdjQe.png&h=e67a0b8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f7b61de8dcaf2b28d166780aee87aaf50381a65","tid":2417828,"uid":2